uacme (1.0.10-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Added secp384r1 EC support
    - -b, --bits option accepts 256 or 384 for EC keys
  * enforce multiple of 8 RSA key size
  * improved acme_get and acme_post verbose logging
  * Implemented retry upon badNonce response according to RFC8555 6.5
  * Fix configure.ac bug for gnutls variant
  * mbedtls: fixed incorrect size of EC signature
  * avoid depending on asciidoc for debian build

 -- Nicola Di Lieto <nicola.dilieto@gmail.com>  Sun, 12 May 2019 18:30:38 +0200

